---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Data Retention & Deletion Policy - RoyalPrompt" description="Data retention and deletion policy for RoyalPrompt - Learn how long we keep your data and how to request deletion.">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12">
    <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-8">Data Retention & Deletion Policy</h1>
      
      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">
        <strong>Last updated:</strong> December 2024
      </p>

      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-8">
        This Data Retention & Deletion Policy explains how long RoyalPrompt retains your personal data and how you can request its deletion. This policy supplements our <a href="/privacy" class="text-royal-600 hover:text-royal-700 underline">Privacy Policy</a>.
      </p>

      <div class="bg-blue-50 border-l-4 border-blue-400 p-6 mb-8">
        <div class="flex">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0">
            <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-blue-400" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M18 10a8 8 0 11-16 0 8 8 0 0116 0zm-7-4a1 1 0 11-2 0 1 1 0 012 0zM9 9a1 1 0 000 2v3a1 1 0 001 1h1a1 1 0 100-2v-3a1 1 0 00-1-1H9z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div class="ml-3">
            <p class="text-sm text-blue-700">
              <strong>Your Right to Deletion:</strong> You have the right to request deletion of your personal data at any time. We will process your request within 30 days unless we have a legal obligation to retain the data.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">1. Data Retention Periods</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
        We retain different types of data for different periods based on their purpose and legal requirements:
      </p>

      <h3 class="text-xl font-medium text-gray-900 mt-6 mb-3">1.1 Contact Form Data</h3>
      <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-lg mb-4">
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-2"><strong>Retention Period:</strong> Up to 3 years</p>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-2"><strong>Data Types:</strong> Name, email address, subject, message content</p>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-2"><strong>Purpose:</strong> Customer service, support history, legal compliance</p>
        <p class="text-gray-600"><strong>Deletion Trigger:</strong> Upon request, after 3 years, or when no longer needed for customer service</p>
      </div>

      <h3 class="text-xl font-medium text-gray-900 mt-6 mb-3">1.2 Device Usage Data</h3>
      <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-lg mb-4">
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-2"><strong>Retention Period:</strong> Up to 2 years</p>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-2"><strong>Data Types:</strong> Device ID, usage statistics, app interactions, preferences</p>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-2"><strong>Purpose:</strong> Service improvement, analytics, personalization</p>
        <p class="text-gray-600"><strong>Deletion Trigger:</strong> Upon request, after 2 years, or when device is inactive for 1 year</p>
      </div>

      <h3 class="text-xl font-medium text-gray-900 mt-6 mb-3">1.3 App Content (User-Generated)</h3>
      <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-lg mb-4">
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-2"><strong>Retention Period:</strong> Until deleted by user or app uninstall</p>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-2"><strong>Data Types:</strong> Created prompts, favorites, collections, custom content</p>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-2"><strong>Purpose:</strong> Provide app functionality, user experience</p>
        <p class="text-gray-600"><strong>Deletion Trigger:</strong> User deletion, app uninstall, or upon request</p>
      </div>

      <h3 class="text-xl font-medium text-gray-900 mt-6 mb-3">1.4 Technical Logs</h3>
      <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-lg mb-4">
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-2"><strong>Retention Period:</strong> Up to 1 year</p>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-2"><strong>Data Types:</strong> IP addresses, error logs, crash reports, access logs</p>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-2"><strong>Purpose:</strong> Security, debugging, performance monitoring</p>
        <p class="text-gray-600"><strong>Deletion Trigger:</strong> Automatic after 1 year, or upon request (if not needed for security)</p>
      </div>

      <h3 class="text-xl font-medium text-gray-900 mt-6 mb-3">1.5 Website Analytics</h3>
      <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-lg mb-4">
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-2"><strong>Retention Period:</strong> Up to 26 months (Google Analytics default)</p>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-2"><strong>Data Types:</strong> Page views, user behavior, referral sources, device info</p>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-2"><strong>Purpose:</strong> Website optimization, user experience improvement</p>
        <p class="text-gray-600"><strong>Deletion Trigger:</strong> Automatic after 26 months, or upon request</p>
      </div>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">2. Automatic Deletion</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
        We automatically delete data in the following circumstances:
      </p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-600 mb-4">
        <li><strong>Expired Retention Periods:</strong> Data is automatically deleted when it reaches the end of its retention period</li>
        <li><strong>Inactive Devices:</strong> Device data is deleted after 1 year of inactivity</li>
        <li><strong>App Uninstall:</strong> User-generated content is deleted when the app is uninstalled (if not synced)</li>
        <li><strong>Account Closure:</strong> All associated data is deleted when an account is closed</li>
        <li><strong>Legal Requirements:</strong> Data may be deleted earlier if required by law</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">3. Requesting Data Deletion</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
        You can request deletion of your personal data at any time. Here's how:
      </p>

      <h3 class="text-xl font-medium text-gray-900 mt-6 mb-3">3.1 How to Request Deletion</h3>
      <div class="bg-green-50 border border-green-200 p-6 rounded-lg mb-4">
        <h4 class="font-semibold text-green-800 mb-2">Email Request</h4>
        <p class="text-green-700 mb-2">Send an email to: <strong>privacy@royalprompt.app</strong></p>
        <p class="text-green-700 mb-2">Subject line: <strong>"Data Deletion Request"</strong></p>
        <p class="text-green-700 mb-4">Include: Your device ID (if available) and specify which data you want deleted</p>
        
        <h4 class="text-green-800 font-semibold mb-2">Contact Form</h4>
        <p class="text-green-700">Use our <a href="/contact" class="text-green-600 hover:text-green-800 underline">contact form</a> and select "Data Deletion Request" as the subject.</p>
      </div>

      <h3 class="text-xl font-medium text-gray-900 mt-6 mb-3">3.2 What Happens After Your Request</h3>
      <ol class="list-decimal pl-6 text-gray-600 mb-4">
        <li><strong>Verification:</strong> We may need to verify your identity to protect your privacy</li>
        <li><strong>Processing:</strong> We will process your request within 30 days</li>
        <li><strong>Confirmation:</strong> We will confirm what data has been deleted</li>
        <li><strong>Exceptions:</strong> We will explain if any data must be retained for legal reasons</li>
      </ol>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">4. Data That Cannot Be Deleted</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
        In some cases, we may be legally required to retain certain data even after a deletion request:
      </p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-600 mb-4">
        <li><strong>Legal Obligations:</strong> Data required for tax, accounting, or regulatory compliance</li>
        <li><strong>Dispute Resolution:</strong> Data needed for ongoing legal proceedings</li>
        <li><strong>Fraud Prevention:</strong> Data required to prevent fraud or abuse</li>
        <li><strong>Public Safety:</strong> Data needed to protect public safety or security</li>
        <li><strong>Anonymized Data:</strong> Data that has been anonymized and cannot be linked to you</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">5. Data Backup and Recovery</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
        We maintain secure backups of our systems for disaster recovery purposes. These backups may contain copies of your data:
      </p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-600 mb-4">
        <li><strong>Backup Retention:</strong> Backups are typically retained for 30-90 days</li>
        <li><strong>Automatic Deletion:</strong> Deleted data will be removed from backups during the next backup cycle</li>
        <li><strong>Recovery Access:</strong> Backups are only accessed for system recovery, not for data restoration</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">6. Third-Party Data</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
        Some of your data may be processed by third-party services. We will:
      </p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-600 mb-4">
        <li>Request deletion from third-party services when you request data deletion</li>
        <li>Ensure third parties comply with their own data retention policies</li>
        <li>Provide you with information about which third parties have your data</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">7. Data Minimization</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
        We follow the principle of data minimization, meaning we:
      </p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-600 mb-4">
        <li>Only collect data that is necessary for our services</li>
        <li>Regularly review and delete unnecessary data</li>
        <li>Use anonymized or pseudonymized data when possible</li>
        <li>Implement automatic data purging systems</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">8. Your Rights</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
        In addition to deletion, you have the right to:
      </p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-600 mb-4">
        <li><strong>Access:</strong> Request a copy of all data we have about you</li>
        <li><strong>Rectification:</strong> Correct inaccurate or incomplete data</li>
        <li><strong>Portability:</strong> Receive your data in a machine-readable format</li>
        <li><strong>Restriction:</strong> Limit how we process your data</li>
        <li><strong>Objection:</strong> Object to certain types of data processing</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">9. Contact Us</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
        If you have questions about data retention or want to request data deletion, please contact us:
      </p>
      <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-lg">
        <p class="text-gray-700">
          <strong>Email:</strong> privacy@royalprompt.app<br>
          <strong>Subject:</strong> Data Retention/Deletion Inquiry<br>
          <strong>Response Time:</strong> Within 30 days<br>
          <strong>Address:</strong> RoyalPrompt Privacy Team<br>
          [Your Company Address]
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-yellow-50 border-l-4 border-yellow-400 p-6 mt-8">
        <div class="flex">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0">
            <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-yellow-400" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M8.257 3.099c.765-1.36 2.722-1.36 3.486 0l5.58 9.92c.75 1.334-.213 2.98-1.742 2.98H4.42c-1.53 0-2.493-1.646-1.743-2.98l5.58-9.92zM11 13a1 1 0 11-2 0 1 1 0 012 0zm-1-8a1 1 0 00-1 1v3a1 1 0 002 0V6a1 1 0 00-1-1z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div class="ml-3">
            <p class="text-sm text-yellow-700">
              <strong>Important:</strong> Once data is deleted, it cannot be recovered. Please ensure you have backed up any important information before requesting deletion. If you're unsure about what data will be deleted, please contact us first.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
